Word list data license
=======================

The raw word lists downloaded into this directory (see README.md) are
third-party data, NOT application code. They are licensed separately from the
rest of the repository (which is under the Counter-Limitation License, see
/LICENSE.md). The CLL does NOT apply to these files, nor to the compiled
lexicons in Resources/Lexicons/ derived from them.

  <xx>_50k.txt        hermitdave/FrequencyWords (OpenSubtitles 2018)
                      CC-BY-SA 4.0
                      https://github.com/hermitdave/FrequencyWords
                      https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

  <xx>_sentences.tsv  Tatoeba sentence exports
                      CC-BY 2.0 FR
                      https://tatoeba.org/en/downloads
                      https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/fr/deed.en

The unigram source is CC-BY-SA 4.0; any adaptation (including the compiled
*.clex / *.cngm in Resources/Lexicons/) must be distributed under CC-BY-SA 4.0.
Changes are documented in Tools/GenerateLexicons.swift. Attribution for all
sources is shown in the app's About screen.
